<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Чат</title>
    <style>
        body { margin: 0; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; background: #e5ddd5; display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 20px; }
        .chat { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; background: #efe7dd; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
        .header { background: #ededed; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1px solid white; }
        .messages { padding: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; overflow-y: auto; max-height: 80vh; }
        
        .row { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 10px; max-width: 80%; }
        .row.left { align-self: flex-start; }
        .row.right { align-self: flex-end; flex-direction: row-reverse; }
        
        .avatar { 
            width: 40px; 
            height: 40px; 
            border-radius: 50%; 
            background-color: #ccc; 
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 24px; 
            flex-shrink: 0;
            user-select: none;
        }
        
        .bubble { background: #fff; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .left .bubble { border-top-left-radius: 0; }
        .right .bubble { background: #dcf8c6; border-top-right-radius: 0; align-items: flex-end; }
        
        .name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .left .name { color: pink; }
        .right .name { color: green; }
        
        .text { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .time { font-size: 10px; color: gray; text-align: right; }
        .right .time { color: green; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="chat">
        <div class="header">Групповой чат</div>
        <div class="messages">
            <div class="row left">
                <div class="avatar">👩</div>
                <div class="bubble">
                    <span class="name">Anna</span>
                    <span class="text">Привет! Кто идет на конференцию?</span>
                    <span class="time">10:15</span>
                </div>
            </div>

         
            <div class="row right">
                <div class="avatar">👨</div>
                <div class="bubble">
                    <span class="name">Я</span>
                    <span class="text">Я буду! Уже зарегистрировался.</span>
                    <span class="time">10:17</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            
            <div class="row left">
                <div class="avatar">👤</div>
                <div class="bubble">
                    <span class="name">Maxim</span>
                    <span class="text">Я тоже планирую. Во сколько начало?</span>
                    <span class="time">10:20</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row right">
                <div class="avatar">👨</div>
                <div class="bubble">
                    <span class="name">Я</span>
                    <span class="text">В 19:00. Встречаемся у входа за 15 мин.</span>
                    <span class="time">10:22</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row left">
                <div class="avatar">👩</div>
                <div class="bubble">
                    <span class="name">Anna</span>
                    <span class="text">Отлично! До встречи 😉</span>
                    <span class="time">10:25</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

